snippet.title: Rushdown Rivals -  Update Trailer (CO-OP Newgrounds Beat Em' Up Feat. Cassette Girl, Hank, FNF)
snippet.description:
THIS WILL BE A FAN-MADE GAME. WE DO NOT OWN ANY OF THE CHARACTERS. ORIGINAL CREATORS IN THE CREDITS BELOW. ANYTHING SEEN HERE COULD BE SUBJECT TO CHANGE.

==============================================================================



Happy Pico Day 2022! After months of work, we finally are able to reveal what we had in store. It was supposed to be just Cassette girl, but.... we kinda got carried away with more ideas lol. The wait will absolutely be worth it. 



==============================================================================

CREDITS

KEITH GARCES - Director / Animation
SPAGATO - Director / Sound
DIESWYX - Gameplay Music
MILKYPOSSUM - Ending Music
JOECANVAS - Character Portraits
IAMJOEYREX - Background Design



CHARACTER CREDITS

PICO, DARNEL, NENE - Created By Tom Fulp
CASSETTE GIRL - Created By SoftDon
HANK - Created By Krinkels
SON - From Dad 'n Me
GIRLFRIEND - From Friday Night Funkin
PIRATE QUEEN - By Derpidraws
